CMD,OPTION,DESCRIPTION
=============,================,=============================
backup|bkp,status,Current service status
 ,1,Enable service
 ,0,Disable service
 ,load 1/2/3,Load back up version x
 , ,(1 is the most recent)
 ,mode full/channel, Set default mode
 ,now full/channel,Do back up right now
 ,reset,Reinitialize folder structure
 ,restore,Undo reset
cron,ls,Show current cron job settings
 ,set epg/bkp,Change choosen cron setting
service,status,Current service status
 ,1,Enable service
 ,0,Disable service
setup|conf,-,Run easyEPG Script
version|ver|v,-,Show version of easyEPG
xml,-,List existing xml files